<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śrījananālayuṁḍu budhasēvyuṁḍu vē 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>muṁḍu sadguṇuṇḍu mātājanakadvaya 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁbunaku dharmmuvugā śaśimauḷi dharmmi 
<lb n="4"/>yai rājitacaṁdramauḷikiṁ diraṁbugaṁ bāmu 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>lapāṭaṁ beṭṭe satpūjita mai mahi nnegaḍa 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṁ bolpagucunna yakhaṇḍadīpamunu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> vā 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>raka yā niśākaradivākara mai canaṁgā śakābda 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>mulu dhāruṇi vārddhi naṁdda divitārakanādha 
<lb n="9"/>mitaṁbugā mahini gaurata nuttarāyaṇamu 
<lb n="10"/>gāramai yeṟagāṁkkaputruṁ ḍu tsāritadō 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṣapuṁjamu vicāraparuṇḍu dharātalaṁbu 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nanu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied> sakavarṣaṁbulu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> 1094 ṇḍayuttarā 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>yaṇasaṁkrāṁtti vēmināyakuṁḍu damataṁḍṛ 
<lb n="14"/>yeṟṟamaraḍḍikiṁ jāmasānki dharmmavu 
<lb n="15"/>gā mūlasthāna śrīmallikhārjuna dēvaraku nakha 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>ṇḍadīpamunakuṁ beṭṭinagoṟiyalu 55 vīni 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ṁ jēkoni sōmabōyinikoḍku gāde danapu 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>trānu pautrikamu nityamāneṁḍu neyi 
<lb n="19"/>vōyaṁggalavāṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

